{"tid":2237440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"食完黃店有咩做？同學仔係銅鑼灣東角道搞咗個抗爭攝影展街站!！","createTime":"2020-10-10T09:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T20:18:07.000Z","uid":140538,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7e291d98f73cd6bc11a6288548d886f4741759","tid":2237440,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"010黃店感謝祭，食飽飽想消化下有咩做？<br />\n不如去睇下同學仔搞既初心攝影展啦👀支持同路人🖐👆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/stpoliticism/74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpoliticism%2F74&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=170f3ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stpoliticism/74</a><br />\n抗爭攝影展【初心&mdash;四季不變】<br />\n[是次攝影展將以街站形式展出]<br />\n日期：<br />\n10.10 銅鑼灣 &mdash; 東角道<br />\n10.11 朗屏 &mdash;黨鐵B出口（聯同天水連線 ）<br />\n10.17 西環 &mdash; 黨鐵C出口<br />\n10.18旺角 &mdash; 豉油街<br />\n10.24荃灣 &mdash; 地皇廣場<br />\n10.25沙田 &mdash; 新城市中庭<br />\n抗爭攝影展【初心&mdash;四季不變】<br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/st_politicism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fst_politicism&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=d11b0a3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/st_politicism</a><br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://fb.me/stpoliticism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fstpoliticism&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=79848324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.me/stpoliticism</a><br />\nTelegram： <a href=\"https://t.me/stpoliticism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpoliticism&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=80f99b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stpoliticism</a><br />\n<br />\n#賢學思政 #抗爭攝影展 #初心四季不變<br />\n#銅鑼灣 #朗屏 #西環 #旺角 #荃灣 #沙田<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n🔈民間記者會現有官方帳號：<br />\n<br />\nOfficial webpage: <a href=\"http://www.citizenspc.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=3a8c95cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.citizenspc.org</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=b6a75709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://fb.me/hkercpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fhkercpc&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=77df1be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/hkercpc</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=3cf4455a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2OVdv6T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OVdv6T&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=d58010b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2OVdv6T</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/citizenspc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2Fcitizenspc&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=38903483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.twitter.com/citizenspc</a>"},{"pid":"9aefee2388308d06b4116e34da319e3040c030fc","tid":2237440,"uid":140538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"抗爭攝影展【初心&mdash;四季不變】<br />\n <br />\n「不要因年月久了便忘記初心，皆因那是我們最珍貴的寶藏。」<br />\n<br />\n二零一九年，用血汗交織的四季。<br />\n二零一九年，歲月不能抹滅的四季。<br />\n二零一九年，那必定載入史冊的四季。<br />\n<br />\n「初心易得，始終難守。」<br />\n<br />\n這一年，我們懷著初心，鐵骨錚錚，英勇奮戰，在街頭撒下的熱血，那是無論如何都不能抹滅的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n但在光陰的流逝中，我們漸漸在迷霧裏丟失了方向，面對步步逼近的不義政權，我們的初心<br />\n逐漸動搖。<br />\n<br />\n但我們知道，人民與政權的對抗，必定是漫長且常有所失望，亦從來都不是一朝一夕的事情。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我們必須在未來抗爭路途中緊守初心，至死不渝，直至那天，我們能建立民族新的秩序和制度。<br />\n<br />\n「我們的初心，那赤子之心」<br />\n<br />\n我們希望，藉此展覽，令眾人憶起昔日，令我們能懷著赤子之心，在未來一個個四季中，繼續編寫歷史的新章節。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n「是次攝影展將以街站形式展出」"},{"pid":"4d2d99cb139b39686b8bd851e2d41307a7429243","tid":2237440,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abdeb3843a025f9d5799d58d611ac56058d0af2","tid":2237440,"uid":4812,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:26:57.000Z","msg":"推 頭先行完 好少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534d4c232b2c1360de5690760274db6a8f349c2","tid":2237440,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d2d99cb139b39686b8bd851e2d41307a7429243","tid":2237440,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3209db9f587a2bcc1df23322cd68ede422ae4a3","tid":2237440,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi